Any suggestions or fixes?  I am DL this 9.0 in hopes of circumventing that annoying expiration.  AlisaK2000@aol.com

Acrobat isn't part of CS4 really, it has it's own protection.
Try this mod if you'd like, but I can't assure you that you computer won't remember older settings/registrations.

Adobe should provide a cleaner on their website, look for it.

Good luck !
